        <h1 class="animate-in">Aditya Vikram Singh<br><span class="gradient-text">Quantitative Strategy Researcher</span></h1>
        <p class="hero-thesis animate-in delay-1">
            I believe robust strategies are built on honest failure analysis, not polished backtests. 
            My research focuses on volatility surface arbitrage, systematic options selling, and 
